): 
<typeStatus box="[346,448,666,692]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">holotype</typeStatus>
and 
<number box="[506,535,666,692]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" value="18.0">18</number>
<typeStatus box="[543,655,666,692]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">paratypes</typeStatus>
female imagos from 
<collectingCountry box="[907,1028,666,692]" name="Argentina" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Argentina</collectingCountry>
: Salta, Aguas Blancas, Estancia El Arrayazal, 
<date box="[281,417,704,730]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" value="1981-12-09">
